Short:    Fullscreen spectrometer plugin for AmigaAMP
Author:   Thomas Wenzel
Type:     mus/play
Version:  1.4

Homepage
--------
http://www.amigaamp.de/


Usage
-----
Just start the plugin by clicking on its icon while AmigaAMP is running
in skin mode.


Key assignments
---------------
ESC  -  quit
F1   -  show 1024 lines
F2   -  show 512 lines (default)
F3   -  show 256 lines


Tooltypes
---------
AUTOIDLE  = YES or NO
            enable or disable the auto-idle function (see v1.2 entry in history)

TRACKINFO = TOP, BOTTOM or OFF
            place to display the track info line (top of the screen, bottom
            of the screen or not at all)


Minimum requirements
--------------------
AmigaOS 3.0
68030-50MHz processor
AmigaAMP 2.3
CyberGraphX 3
Graphics card capable of displaying 640x480 / 256 colours


History
-------
v1.0 - initial release

v1.1 - screen close bug fixed

v1.2 - The plugin will now automatically switch to idle mode when its window
       is deactivated (click on another screen)
     - PPC version included (ELF executable for PowerUP)

v1.3 - various optimizations
     - configuration tooltypes added

v1.4 - some minor bugfixes


More info
---------
See AmigaAMP's documentation
